-- 2010-09-29T09:44:43Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-29/berlusconi-says-government-to-accelerate-plans-to-build-sicily-bridge.html
Italian Prime Minister Silvio
Berlusconi said a plan for the Messina Strait bridge linking
Sicily to mainland Italy will be ready by December, speaking in
Parliament today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
